    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina miserante clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">[r]eges</rs>. Si nostrorum fidelium peticionibus
                        consensum prebemus, devotiores eos esse in nostro servitio non vacillamus.
                        Quapropter omnium sanctae Dei Eclesiae nostrorumque fidelium noverit
                        presentia, qualiter <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops"
                            ref="#people/1531">Boso</persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2002 #juridical_persons/223">sanctae
                                <placeName ref="#places/43">Placentine</placeName>
                            eclesiae</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">presul</rs> supplex adiit nostram <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >deprecans</rs> clementiam, ut Dei pro amore suaque dilectione donaremus
                            <rs key="#Canons">canonicis</rs> de <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Houses #Mansi #Forests #Hay/fodder #Collegiate_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/253">Beati Antonini</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansum</rs> unum in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Mansi #Forests #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/477"><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Mansi #Forests #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Ancariano</geogName></placeName>, laboratum per <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Andreas">Andream</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">massarium</rs>. Domini igitur amorem suamque
                        considerantes dilectionem atque peticionem, tradimus, donamus atque
                        concedimus illis prenominatam terram in Ancariano, que quondam fuit
                            <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Berteritus"
                            >Berteriti</name></persName> cuiusdam nostri <rs key="#Royal_slave"
                            >servi</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in eorum ius et dominium</rs> transfunndimus
                        ac delegamus, ut habeant, teneant firmiterque possideant, habeant etiam
                        potestatem tenendi, commutandi, fruendi sicut de cetera terra, que in eorum
                        iure pert[i]nere videtur, habent. Concedimus illis ita[que] prefatum mansum
                        cum omni integritate, cum <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs> videlicet, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs> et omnibus rebus que ibi
                        pertinere videntur in integrum. Si quis igitur huius pr[ecep]ti violat[or
                        exstit]erit, sci[a]t se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">[au]ri optimi libras
                            C</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem nostrae kammere</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem prefatis
                            canonicis</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus
                        observetur, manibus propriis r[obo]rantes in calce anulo nostro iussimus
                        insigniri. Signa serenissimorum (MF) (MF) Hugonis et Lotharii regum.
                            <persName key="#Bishops"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> in
                        Dei nomine <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> regio iussu recognovi et
                        subscripsi (SR) (SI). Data VIII kal. mar., anno dominicae incarnationis
                        DCCCCXLIIII, regni autem donni Hugonis invictissimi regis XX, et Lotharii
                        item regis XV, indic. IIII. Actum <placeName ref="#places/43"
                            >Placentiae</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
